Hi, I would like to contribute to the rustc.
To find something to work on, I looked at open issues, and I found this one: https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/86868 which piqued my interest. I read the relevant zulip topic, but I am still not sure what needs to be done. It seems like @arora-aman worked on this, but the issue is still open?
I read that discussion, should I ask my questions there ? I don't know the etiquettes of Zulip :smile:
